## ✅ What IS Working Correctly

- **Authentication flow** (register → OTP → login → logout → refresh) — logic sound
- **Role-based access guards** ([authenticate](file:///d:/Reimvide/pashudhan%20shuraksha/Insurance-Website/Backend/middleware/auth.middleware.js#4-83) + [authorize](file:///d:/Reimvide/pashudhan%20shuraksha/Insurance-Website/Backend/middleware/auth.middleware.js#118-137) middleware) — correct
- **Multi-level commission calculation** (up to 5 parent levels) — correct hierarchy traversal
- **Policy approval workflow** (admin approve → PDF generate → email → commissions) — mostly correct
- **Cookie-based auth** (HTTP-only cookies + cross-tab sync) — well implemented
- **File upload middleware** (multer, type filters, size limits) — correct
- **Razorpay payment signature verification** in [verifyPayment](file:///d:/Reimvide/pashudhan%20shuraksha/Insurance-Website/AgentFrontend/src/services/api.service.js#169-173) — correct HMAC SHA-256
- **Policy renewal logic** (marks old policy RENEWED) — correct in both customer + agent flows
- **KYC document handling** on User and Agent models — correct structure
- **Pagination math** on admin list endpoints — correct
- **CORS configuration** with env-based custom origins — correct

---

> 📌 **Recommended Fix Priority:** #1 → #2 → #3 → #4 → #8 → #6 → #7 → #9 → #15 → #16 → #18
